---
import PageLayout from "@layouts/PageLayout.astro";
const title = "Space Tourism Website";
---

<PageLayout title={title}>
  <div
    class="background-img"
    slot="background"
    style={`--bg-image-desktop: url("/images/home/background-home-desktop.jpg");--bg-image-tablet: url("/images/home/background-home-tablet.jpg");--bg-image-mobile: url("/images/home/background-home-mobile.jpg")`}
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-40 flex flex-col items-center lg:flex-row lg:justify-between gap-20 md:gap-36 py-10 md:py-24 lg:pt-40"
  >
    <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
      <span
        class="text-primary uppercase text-base md:text-xl lg:text-[28px] leading-none tracking-[2.7px] md:tracking-[3.375px] lg:tracking-[4.725px]"
        >So, you want to travel to</span
      >
      <h1
        class="mt-4 md:mt-6 font-bellefair uppercase text-[5rem] md:text-[150px] leading-[100px] md:leading-none"
      >
        space
      </h1>
      <p
        class="mt-4 md:mt-6 font-barlow text-primary text-[15px] leading-[25px] max-w-md md:text-base md:leading-[28px] lg:text-lg lg:leading-8"
      >
        Let’s face it; if you want to go to space, you might as well genuinely
        go to outer space and not hover kind of on the edge of it. Well sit
        back, and relax because we’ll give you a truly out of this world
        experience!
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="explore_btn bg-light rounded-full cursor-pointer w-[150px] h-[150px] md:w-[242px] md:h-[242px] lg:w-[274px] lg:h-[274px] grid place-items-center shrink-0 lg:self-end"
    >
      <span
        class="text-dark text-xl md:text-[2rem] uppercase tracking-[1.25px] md:tracking-[2px]"
        >Explore</span
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
